    "description": "<p>Momentous mountains that can barrel through foes and stay in the thick of it, keeping heat off allies.</p>",
    "attacks": "<p><strong>Inflict Violence: Charge.</strong> Move 2 in a straight line and then attack an adjacent enemy with Bravery. If the Juggernaut moved all 2 tiles, they <strong>taunt</strong> the enemy until the end of their next riff.</p><p><strong>Gambits</strong> [[/r d4]]</p><p><strong>1:</strong> Rush &gt; Inflict Violence &gt; Inflict Violence</p><p><strong>2:</strong> Rush &gt; <strong>Grapple [1]:</strong> Choose an adjacent enemy and slide them into any other tile adjacent to the Juggernaut, then the next attack against them gains +1d. &gt; Inflict Violence</p><p><strong>3:</strong> Rush &gt; <strong>Trample [1]:</strong> Rush, moving through enemies. Any enemy you move through is <strong>pushed 1</strong> and if they collide, are <strong>stunned.</strong> &gt; Inflict Violence</p><p><strong>4:</strong> Rush &gt; <strong>Shock Wave [2]:</strong> Attack all enemies in an area (Blast 4) and then <strong>slow</strong> them.</p>",
    "speed": 5,
    "jump": 1,
